      <title>面包屑导航样式重构：从图标繁复到极简对齐</title>
      <link>https://www.261449.xyz/blog/%E9%9D%A2%E5%8C%85%E5%B1%91%E5%AF%BC%E8%88%AA%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F%E9%87%8D%E6%9E%84%E4%BB%8E%E5%9B%BE%E6%A0%87%E7%B9%81%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B0%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%80%E5%AF%B9%E9%BD%90/</link>
